OL,3,CNigel Farage to compete with record 33
OL,4,Ccandidates in Clacton by-election
OL,6,FNigel Farage will compete with a
OL,7,Frecord 33 other candidates in the
OL,8,FClacton by-election, despite several
OL,9,Fpolitical parties refusing to stand.
OL,11,FThe Reform UK leader triggered the by-
OL,12,Felection in what he called a "people
OL,13,Fversus the establishment" contest,
OL,14,Fprotesting against media and
OL,15,Fparliamentary scrutiny of his finances.
OL,17,FLabour, the Conservatives, the Liberal
OL,18,FDemocrats and the Green Party have all
OL,19,Fboycotted the by-election and said
OL,20,Fthey will not be putting forward a
OL,21,Fcandidate.
OL,26,@uD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
