OL,3,CNigel Farage to compete with record 33
OL,4,Ccandidates in Clacton by-election
OL,6,FHowever, the public will still have 34
OL,7,Fpeople to choose from when they head
OL,8,Fto polling stations on August 13,
OL,9,FTendring District Council confirmed.
OL,11,FIan Davidson, Chief Executive of
OL,12,FTendring District Council, posted the
OL,13,FStatement of Persons Nominated for the
OL,14,FClacton by-election on the doors of
OL,15,FClacton Town Hall.
OL,17,FAside from Farage, voters can choose
OL,18,Ffrom the likes of the notorious Count
OL,19,FBinface, Laurence Fox from The Reclaim
OL,20,FParty and Howling Laud Hope from The
OL,21,FOfficial Monster Raving Loony Party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
