OL,3,CNigel Farage to compete with record 33
OL,4,Ccandidates in Clacton by-election
OL,6,FHere is a full list of candidates in
OL,7,Fthe Clacton by-election:
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FThis is believed to have broken the
OL,15,Frecord for the greatest number of
OL,16,Fcandidates in a parliamentary contest,
OL,17,Fbeating the Haltemprice and Howden by-
OL,18,Felection in July 2008 which had 26
OL,19,Fcandidates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
