CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1784337480
OL,3,CNigel Farage to compete with record 33
OL,4,Ccandidates in Clacton by-election
OL,6,FFarage has insisted he has not done
OL,7,Fanything wrong, and said the gifts and
OL,8,Fbenefits are exempt because they were
OL,9,Ffor personal use, but chose to resign
OL,10,Ffrom his seat to let the "people of
OL,11,FClacton be the judges" of his actions.
OL,13,F"It's a chance to stick two fingers up
OL,14,Fto the entire establishment to frankly
OL,15,Ftell them where to go, and that is why
OL,16,FI will be putting my name forward to
OL,17,Fstand in this by-election. I will
OL,18,Ffight to win," Farage said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
